name: Cute Kitten Photos Puzzle
description:
If you are a Cat Lover you will love this game. Have fun with the classic 3x3 puzzle with beautiful kitty images.

Accept the challenge and build a beautiful kitty image in no more than 100 seconds. Is that easy? Then it's time to prove it and put together your first puzzle of a beautiful kitten.

Discover the collection of the best kitten images in Kitten Puzzle. The game created especially for cat lovers!
